snippet.textDisplay:
For Seedhe Maut fans 👇

(Encore)
Bura na maane holi hai raja
Gusse ko peeja, bol rang ki bhasha
Jahan se main aata waha aaye din
Koyi kiska gubbaara maare
Lekin aaj din pyaara
Kyonki aaj tyahar aur
Mood dildaar dikhe bhaiyo ka 4 aur
Gulal dala jeb mein hai pucchhe pade 4 aur
Hanji aaj briz ki holi bonri hardcore


Park aur moholle ki galliyon mein bhagre hai bheege
Papa ke matho pe rango ke tikke
Sab gaare dil se aur sab rangeen hai
Na koi kiske upar na koi kisike neechhe

(Calm)
Bheega aaya ghar mein gujiya khane oh
Wapas bhara gubbaro mein paani oh
Hai khili gilli mitti mein bhi holi ooh
Rango ke neechhe ni dikhai jaati
Hamari woh zidd hai
Rang jo na mete bhaang se na hile
Launde katil hai
Jahan bhi ho rahi tafri bade shamil hai
Bahana chahiye bas khulegi bottlein
Aaj hawa mein rang hai toh roko samay
Iss bhole mein dum hai toh beete paare

Tyaharo pe yaad aati hai ek ghar ki hai
Jahan bepanwah pyaar hai humein bhook hai
Toh bhole rah lunga bhookha
Nishana kabhi na chuke
Jhoomo khele jayo koi ni dekh raha hai
Picchhkari moti hai koi nehi bas paaye
Hai muh pe pakka rang aur use pata bhi ni bhai
Tera bhai SEEDHE MAUT! 🔥💥 @seedhemaut
